In the terminal:

1. Start a new screen session:
screen -S mysession

2. Run your command within the screen session:
python /home/marthaj/Documents/MAENEW/segmentation/train.py /home/marthaj/Documents/MAENEW/segmentation/mae_vit-base-p16_8xb512-amp-coslr-300e_in1k.py

3.Detach from the screen session (without stopping the process) by pressing Ctrl+A followed by D.

4. To reattach to the session later, use:
screen -r mysession
